OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef has this special report
OL,10,FA headteacher has turned to technology
OL,11,Fto try and stop students skipping
OL,12,Fclass to vape in the toilets.
OL,14,FTony McCabe says pupils as young as 11
OL,15,Fare starting at his secondary school,
OL,16,FSt Joseph's RC High School in Horwich,
OL,17,Fin Greater Manchester, addicted to
OL,18,Fvapes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
