OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FMr McCabe said: "The vape sensors were
OL,8,Ffitted into every single toilet
OL,9,Fcubicle.
OL,11,F"The very first day that they were
OL,12,Ffitted they went off 112 times which
OL,13,Ftells us that some young people could
OL,14,Fnot last an hour without needing to
OL,15,Fcome and use the toilets so they could
OL,16,Fuse a vape."
OL,18,FThe sensors can detect vaping,
OL,19,Fcannabis and traditional smoking.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
