OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FIt enables schools to monitor and act
OL,8,Fin real-time, identifying problem
OL,9,Flocations, reducing classroom
OL,10,Fdisruption and aiming to improve
OL,11,Fstudents' health.
OL,13,FThe school decided to install them
OL,14,Fafter several students needed hospital
OL,15,Ftreatment after using contaminated
OL,16,Fvapes - including one who stopped
OL,17,Fbreathing for a period of time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
