OL,7,FPupils are not punished if they are
OL,8,Ffound with a vape and are instead
OL,9,Fgiven help to beat their addiction, Mr
OL,10,FMcCabe said.
OL,12,FThe school's focus is on student
OL,13,Fsafety and educating both children and
OL,14,Fparents about the risks of vaping.
OL,16,FBut despite this, some children still
OL,17,Ftry and hid their vapes in their
OL,18,Fshoes, hair and clothing.
OL,20,FGamal Fahnbulleh spoke to John Dunne
OL,21,Ffrom the UK Vaping Industry Association
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
