OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FThe number of children who vape has
OL,8,Ftripled over the past three years,
OL,9,Ffigures from the Department of Health
OL,10,Fand Social Care show - with around 9%
OL,11,Fof 11 to 15 years olds now vaping.
OL,13,FThe North West has the highest number
OL,14,Fof teenagers who vape, a survey from
OL,15,FGo Smoke Free also found.
OL,17,FNew figures show in Greater Manchester
OL,18,Falone almost half of young people used
OL,19,Fillegal vapes containing THC - a
OL,20,Fsubstance found in cannabis - in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
