OL,7,FThe GM TRENDS report, commissioned by
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Combined Authority
OL,9,F(GMCA) and led by researchers from
OL,10,FManchester Metropolitan University,
OL,11,Falso found 39% stated the vapes had
OL,12,F'got stronger'.
OL,14,FIn September Greater Manchester Police
OL,15,Fseized a haul of illicit and
OL,16,Fcounterfeit vapes believed to be worth
OL,17,Faround #1 million, hidden behind a
OL,18,Fsecret door in a vape shop in Salford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
