OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FHowever police admit it is an ongoing
OL,8,Fbattle to keep potentially harmful
OL,9,Fproducts off the streets.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Rick
OL,12,FThompson from Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice said: "We had our first case of
OL,14,Fa child being hospitalised (because of
OL,15,Fa contaminated vape) in 2019 and as a
OL,16,Fresult we have used Operation Mandrake
OL,17,Fwhich allows us to test substances
OL,18,Fafterwards and put alerts out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
