OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,F"To give you some idea of the scale of
OL,8,Fit - in 2021 the UK Border Agency
OL,9,Fseized around 4,500 illegal vapes.
OL,11,F"In 2023 that was over four and a half
OL,12,Fmillion - so it's a really big issue."
OL,14,FAs well as the obvious dangers of
OL,15,Fillegal vapes police say predators are
OL,16,Fnow using vapes to sexually and
OL,17,Fcriminally exploit children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
