OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Thompson
OL,8,Fadded: "We have seen situations where
OL,9,Fby children are sold or given vapes
OL,10,Ffor free - that might happen once or
OL,11,Ftwice and then after that point they
OL,12,Fare told they owe money and then that
OL,13,Fchild can become debt bonded to an
OL,14,Fexploiter and be told that they have
OL,15,Fto do things.
OL,17,F"That child then feels obliged to do
OL,18,Fthat and that is them then trapped in
OL,19,Fthat circle of exploitation."
